Mislio sam da će biti evo tu (*mislio*). (I thought he would be here.)
Mislio bih da ću biti tu (*mislio*). (I thought I would be here.)
Mislio sam da je to moguće (*mislio*). (I thought that was possible.)
Mislio sam da će oni biti uspešni (*mislio*). (I thought they would be successful.)
